### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@weekMenuId = <pega_el_id_del_menu_semanal>
@weekMenuItemId = <pega_el_id_del_item>
@traditionalDishId = <pega_el_id_del_plato_tradicional>
@healthyDishId = <pega_el_id_del_plato_saludable>
@vegetarianDishId = <pega_el_id_del_plato_vegetariano>

### ─────────────────────────────
### WEEK MENUS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear menú semanal (ADMIN) — week_start_date debe ser lunes
POST {{baseUrl}}/week-menus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "week_start_date": "2026-06-15"
}

###

### Listar todos los menús semanales
GET {{baseUrl}}/week-menus
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener menú semanal por ID (incluye items con platos)
GET {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/one?weekMenuId={{weekMenuId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Consultar el menú del día (platos configurados para esa fecha)
GET {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/menu?date=2026-06-16
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─────────────────────────────
### WEEK MENU ITEMS (días del menú)
### ─────────────────────────────

### Agregar día al menú semanal (ADMIN)
### Requiere IDs de platos ya creados (traditional, healthy, vegetarian)
POST {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/{{weekMenuId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menu_date": "2026-06-16",
  "traditional_dish_id": "{{traditionalDishId}}",
  "healthy_dish_id": "{{healthyDishId}}",
  "vegetarian_dish_id": "{{vegetarianDishId}}"
}

###

### Agregar martes al menú semanal (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/{{weekMenuId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menu_date": "2026-06-17",
  "traditional_dish_id": "{{traditionalDishId}}",
  "healthy_dish_id": "{{healthyDishId}}",
  "vegetarian_dish_id": "{{vegetarianDishId}}"
}

###

### Actualizar item del menú (ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/{{weekMenuId}}/items/{{weekMenuItemId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "traditional_dish_id": "{{traditionalDishId}}",
  "healthy_dish_id": "{{healthyDishId}}",
  "vegetarian_dish_id": "{{vegetarianDishId}}"
}

###

### Eliminar item del menú (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/week-menus/{{weekMenuId}}/items/{{weekMenuItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
